entries.journal_entry_description: The final Gungan artifact that was stolen was broken into six pieces. Find and recover all of them.
entries.journal_entry_title: Recover all Six Pieces of the Scattered Gungan Artifact
entries.task01_item_name: a fragment of a Gungan artifact
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: One fragment is at the Mummer bunker near Theed.
entries.task02_item_name: a fragment of a Gungan artifact
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: One fragment is at the Darkwalker cave near Dee'ja Peak.
entries.task03_item_name: a fragment of a Gungan artifact
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: One fragment was seen in Moenia in the vicinity of the University Hall.
entries.task03_journal_entry_title: Near the University Hall in Moenia
entries.task04_item_name: a fragment of a Gungan artifact
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: One fragment was seen in Keren near the bank.
entries.task05_item_name: a fragment of a Gungan artifact
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: One of the fragments is at the Skaak Tipper hideout near Kaadara.
entries.task05_journal_entry_title: In Skaak Tipper Hideout Near Kaadara
entries.task06_item_name: a fragment of a Gungan artifact
entries.task06_journal_entry_description: One of the fragments is at the Mauler Stronghold.
entries.task07_journal_entry_description: The final gungan artifact was broken into six fragments and scattered to different locations across Naboo. Boss Nass has tracked their general locations.
entries.task07_journal_entry_title: Find the Six Fragments of the Shattered Gungan Artifact
entries.task08_journal_entry_description: Return to Boss Nass and let him know you've recovered all of the fragments of the shattered artifact.
